{"prompt": "Create a website for a mobile app development studio. The design should be cutting-edge, with a bold yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Innovate Mobile Studio</title>\n    <style>\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap');\n\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #FFDA61; /* Bold Yellow */\n            --secondary-color: #FCEBB6; /* Lighter yellow */\n            --text-color-dark: #1a1a1a;\n            --text-color-light: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color-light);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 50px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color-dark);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        header::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: 300;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section#hero {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: 70vh;\n            position: relative;\n            clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 90%, 50% 100%, 0 90%);\n        }\n\n        #hero .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            font-weight: 300;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color-dark);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        section#services {\n            background-color: #2a2a2a;\n            padding-top: 150px; /* To account for the clip-path overlap */\n        }\n\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: #1f1f1f;\n     